description:
#CodingHeart
Using a parametric equation from Wolfram Mathworld (and polar to cartesian coordinate transformation), I draw a heart curve in Processing (Java).

💻 Code: https://thecodingtrain.com/CodingChallenges/134-heart-curve
🎥Next video: https://youtu.be/l5I3Q1JFISE

Links discussed in this video:
🔗 Heart Curve Formulas: http://mathworld.wolfram.com/HeartCurve.html
🎥 Times Tables Cardioid: https://youtu.be/bl3nc_a1nvs
🎥 Polar Coordinates: https://youtu.be/N633bLi_YCw
🎥 Drawing with Fourier Transform and Epicycles: https://youtu.be/MY4luNgGfms
